Year: 1981-2000
Country: Poland
Feature: hand-drawn animation, surrealism
Duration: 1:48:13
Translation: No

Directed by: Piotr Dumala

Description: Animation of the author can be called dumb. In the film drama involving music and natural sounds, no dialogue - poetics, probably inspired by the silent movie, in particular works of brothers Lyumer.Dumala uses in his films, the original author's technique &quot;revival&quot; of images that helps to reproduce the style of the dream. It requires huge investment hermit, solitary work. Many compare it to the monk laboriously rewriting the old scriptures. For the emergence of several frames of a movie lasting a few seconds, the artist requires many hours of non-stop &quot;vytsarapyvanya.&quot; On the day of birth of one second filma.Takaya filigree technique allows us to give the softness of the picture, and every movement of the actor as it leaves an imprint on the surface of the plaster, so that even wiggling your finger clockwise or running are extremely smooth.
Characteristic feature of each and every film of Peter Dumaly - thickening of the supernatural, the irrational accidents, atmospheric phenomena, unexpected actions of the protagonists. Plot and actors aura envelops the strangeness and mystery. Events do not follow from one another, violated the logic and the smooth flow of the narrative. The viewer feels immersed in a dream, full of character and innuendo.
Peter I thought - the creator of exceptional, created the unique author's poetics and style. He himself has repeatedly acknowledged that the process of creation, revitalizing their fantasies feels magician. On the one hand, to deeply feel the beauty of the world, on the other - testifying to the evil around us.
Movies Dumaly - a territory of myth and universal meaning, akin to appear in dreams. The most important thing for him, he said - the gap between imagination and reality. Its elements - the darkness, the night shadows. The world of the artist - a world of a child, amazed and extremely diverse things.



